Content: {t['content']}

Original Context: {t['original_context']}

Target Context: {t['target_context']}

Ensure that the adapted content maintains the original intent and message while making it culturally relevant to the target context. Provide your adapted content in plain text format."""
        return instructions

    @staticmethod
    def score(t: dict, submission: str) -> float | None:
